block content
    h1.content-title
        i.material-icons local_offer
        | Badges
    article.box
        .box-body
            p If you need badge-like labels, you can just use a #[code span] with the class of the color you want: #[code badge-default], #[code badge-success], #[code badge-info], #[code badge-primary], #[code badge-warning] or #[code badge-danger].
            br
            .text-center
                span.badge-default .badge-default
                span.badge-success .badge-success
                span.badge-info .badge-info
                span.badge-primary .badge-primary
                span.badge-warning .badge-warning
                span.badge-danger .badge-danger
            br